notes.note: Rec'd a quote from First Choice Recreation. The odometer reading blank. I asked for the current odometer. They first said it was 2130. Unit travelled backwards 18 km. I called the customer. He confirmed the odometer is at 2148. It hasn't moved since the contract was sold. I also found out that the customer bought the snowmobile one year ago and that he refinanced and had a warranty put on. I told him that the warranty cannot be put on after the fact. He claims he sold the unit back to Bow Ridge, they sold it back to him and put the warranty on. None the less, the problem pre-exists the warranty. Will speak with John as to whether the warranty remains in place. A.H.
